text: Danial Jahić (1 July 1979 – 19 January 2021) was a Serbian athlete. He competed in the men's long jump at the 2000 Summer Olympics. On 19 January 2021, Jahić died at the age of 41 from COVID-19.Preminuo nekadašnji atletičar Danial Jahić ==References== Category:1979 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Serbia Category:Long jumpers Category:Olympians for Serbia
